mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T14:16:06.000Z","msg":"我都想知照xray點令腰背痛更嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T14:32:20.000Z","msg":"會自己嚇自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為其實而家研究已經指出就算冇腰背痛年過30照張xray都好大機會有事（姐係退化呀椎間盤突出咁）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以張片係無法反映出你個腰背痛情況<br />\n有時有d人明明唔係特別痛<br />\n但照完發覺張片好嚴重<br />\n咪拗底唔夠膽郁<br />\n自然outcome咪差囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38e1bd14e8bdaeb7bab6db6bd9a45c6a4ddd1120","tid":746342,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81549c27b7956db0ab2001147ac1f7739aa9e635","tid":746342,"uid":38316,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T14:00:15.000Z","msg":"真係好多黃綠醫生<br />\n仲話係尖子先讀醫生<br />\n內裏一樣有好多係高分低能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T14:36:01.000Z","msg":"香港醫護都係世界頂尖的，佢哋都係考試狀元，紀律性高，如果有出錯，應該係以下原因<br />\n1.港共政府cut資源令醫護工作壓力過大所致；<br />\n2.港共政府收買投共醫生製造醫療事故，然後煽動市民支持引入大陸醫生<br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bqzrBS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bqzrBS</a>"},{"pid":"e128b31281d6425562bf5fd49f9351eb498a46aa","tid":746342,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70b8c432b049a2d28ecdc3cf618790fdeadb23e8","tid":746342,"uid":77406,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T14:07:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出面真係好多黃綠醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜柒都xray ct scan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n公立 私立都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拗柴行得走得都xray<